dc_title_s: Mallard Island at Manahawkin, New Jersey, Stafford Township, Ocean County
dc_description_s: This map shows property lots on Mallard Island that are linked to Monobay Inc Developers. A handwritten inscription indicates this as a tax map.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Township Committee members signed off on the map but the names are not clearly legible.|An inscription states A-13-1 Tax Maps.
